parameters: \C[23]Nicole's room. It's been locked since she left.
\C[23]I should check on Natalie and Mom first.
\C[23]I should check out Mom in her bedroom first.
You're going to end up in the washing machine one day!
\C[23]Where did she go with the laundry basket?!
\C[23]When Mom is sad or stressed, I sometimes find her sitting on top of the running washing machine.
\C[23]I wonder if it has stress relief capabilities?
You're supposed to turn it on!
Ohhhh, of course! Thank you, Big Bro!
Hmm... So I press this button...
I-It makes my thing feel funny...
\C[23]S-She's going to wake the others up!
Mommy likes to sit on the washing machine during the night.
It makes her feel very good.
And now that everyone is asleep... Heh...
\C[23]D-Did she... just... let me watch her...?
